Origin
------
Project Starfish is an original, clean-room project. No third-party source code
or assets are incorporated.

Conceptually inspired by the munder-difflin project
(https://github.com/chaitanyagiri/munder-difflin, MIT). None of that project's
code is used here. That project bundled pixel-art assets under a non-commercial
license (LimeZu FREE VERSION); none of those assets are used either. All Project
Starfish art is original (see docs/ART_PROVENANCE_LEDGER.md).

A CI scan (scripts/ip-denylist-scan.mjs) guards the shippable source under
packages/ against third-party IP tokens.
